comments: After communicating with the Replay Center, the call on the floor of offensive goaltending is confirmed.
Gasol (TOR) sets the screen in Thompson's (GSW) path and does not deliver contact.
Thompson (GSW) extends his arm across Leonard's (TOR) body, but the contact is marginal and does not affect his SQBR.
Lowry (TOR) throws the ball into the backcourt and it is last touched by Toronto.
Cousins (GSW) extends his lower body into VanVleet's (TOR) path while setting the screen, but LAR shows that VanVleet avoids the contact.
Thompson (GSW) legally contests Leonard's (TOR) jump shot attempt.
Cousins (GSW) makes clean contact with the loose ball to deflect it away from Green (TOR) before making marginal contact with his arm.
Cousins (GSW) and Gasol (TOR) briefly engage and separate during the rebound.
Lowry (TOR) briefly grasps Iguodala's (GSW) arm but the contact is marginal and does not affect his FOM.
Gasol (TOR) sets the screen in Iguodala's (GSW) path and absorbs the contact.
LAR and LHH show Cousins (GSW) moves from point A to point B into Gasol (TOR), initiating contact that affects his driving shot attempt.
Gasol (TOR) makes marginal contact with Curry (GSW) after he passes.
Green (TOR) makes marginal contact with Green (GSW) and does not force him into the backcourt.
Green (GSW) steps into the backcourt.
Cousins (GSW) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Lowry (TOR).
Cousins (GSW) makes contact with the ball after it hits the backboard and has a chance to score.
VanVleet (TOR) and Curry (GSW) briefly engage and separate off ball.
Cousins (GSW) delivers contact to VanVleet (TOR) while setting the screen and affects his ability to defend.
Thompson (GSW) and Leonard (TOR) briefly engage and separate off ball.
Green (GSW) briefly places an arm on the side of Gasol (TOR) and the two players engage and disengage.
Iguodala (GSW) makes marginal contact with Leonard (TOR) after the pass.
Green (GSW) legally contests Lowry's (TOR) jump shot attempt.
